{"id": 3083, "genre": 1000, "title": "随着年龄增长，你对时间的感受都有哪些细微的变化？", "description": "一些看起来有点矛盾但有时候确实会发生的体验。（题图来自：iStock ©️ Enis Aksoy）", "record_count": 9242, "comment_count": 24, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191208010539rSjE4XCdfHIJO9Gi.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-12-07T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 6100, "title": "随着年龄增长，你对时间的感受都有哪些细微的变化？", "content": "随着年龄增长，你对时间的感受都有哪些细微的变化？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 350156, "content": "觉得时间过得越来越快，怀疑自己的时间感应模块出了 bug", "image": "img/option/option/20191208002750PYomF6McyVx4qHC8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 350157, "content": "会有“误以为十年前是 1999 年而不是 2009 年”的谜之错觉", "image": "img/option/option/20191208002948jQWi52cNVr4HeRaU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 350158, "content": "下半年一到，就特别容易产生“怎么一年又快过去了”的感触", "image": "img/option/option/20191208003112cy4nB2lZwroGOQSP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 350159, "content": "“成长的感觉”越来越淡，要想一会儿才能意识到自己的年龄", "image": "img/option/option/20191208003421Ys1zoegDOb8VxLdf.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 350160, "content": "对“未来”的概念变得有点模糊（比如觉得 2020 年听起来很遥远）", "image": "img/option/option/20191208004654iF7Te6lxKLQH9RYI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 350161, "content": "每次想到“跟某个人已经认了十几年”，都会有点难以相信", "image": "img/option/option/20191208004907adEMZvC2jsbQitmq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 350162, "content": "生活的重复率似乎变高了，一天的记忆跟一周也没啥差别", "image": "img/option/option/201912080052321XFIu3vkBaJ8R2xS.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 350163, "content": "开始借助工具来标记时间，比如时间管理 app、手机里的照片", "image": "img/option/option/20191208005350twWBkqQSXeP4pZlU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 350164, "content": "好像没这些感觉/我有别的感受", "image": "img/option/option/20191208005731fZ04PctKvrlbEGBA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}